Package mud

Enum Items

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Items>
      • mud.Items

  • public enum Items
extends java.lang.Enum<Items>
    An enum for mass-producing item objects. To make a new Item, first add its name to the enum. Then, in the make() method, where it says switch(this), add a case for the enum value you added. In that case, return the Item you want the enum value to represent/create.
